{"tid":1433453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭最無恥！推d警察出黎受罪！","createTime":"2019-08-08T13:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T13:30:14.000Z","uid":265339,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45e9d6553ce9395f080239e9626b7ef93eec10fe","tid":1433453,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:19:49.000Z","msg":"俾狗逗既時候，試下講「阿sir下話，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我呢就最支持香港警察</span></strong></span>。d廢青成日出黎搞事，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭真係無恥</span></strong></span>，成日推晒d氣俾你地受，離晒大譜！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當有人話話d警察真係好慘既時候，試下講「係囉，乜氣都佢地受晒，連飯都唔得閒食呀！<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭就淨係識龜縮</span></span></strong>，都唔出黎保護下香港警察，呢個政府真係離晒大譜！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當有人話話總之搞事就係唔岩既時候，試下講「係囉，d廢青成日出黎搞事，書又唔去讀。<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭又話做人阿媽，又唔出黎教下仔女</span></span></strong>，都唔知點做人老母」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當有人話成日示威搞差經濟既時候，試下講「係囉，經濟俾人搞到咁差，林鄭政府仲唔出黎搞返好個經濟。DLLM，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4000蚊都未派到手</span></strong></span>，做唔L到野」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他例句<br />\n<br />\n「個個月抖幾廿萬都唔知做左乜，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">影都唔見</span></span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n「出親黎淨係係度照稿讀，淨係講又唔做野，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">識字既都做得特首啦</span></strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n以下歡迎繼續造句<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28cab6428170402e1c50985f758e167d86d4fb9","tid":1433453,"uid":265339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tNgLzgk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtNgLzgk.jpg&h=35665ee3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JvTJ5n0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A